@pres_election

The monarchial election is coming up soon. [? if ccf_in_government = 0 : While the position of Chancellor is typically more important, recent governments have depended on the monarch's emergency decree powers, making the office vital. ?] [? if hitler_deported==0 : The Nazis will run Hitler, while the PCC will run Thälmann. A victory for Hitler would mean the end of parliamentary democracy, and the beginning of an era of unspeakable horrors. ?][? if hitler_deported==1 : Since Hitler has been deported, the Nazis will run Hermann Göring in his stead. He is widely seen as a proxy for Hitler, who, despite his legal persecution, retains a popular base who wishes to see him returned to Germany. Meanwhile, the PCC will run Ernst Thälmann. ?]
[? if sapd_formed: The SAPD, our former leftists, are supporting Thälmann of the PCC, and will likely share an endorsement with the Communists. ?]

# if hitler is deported, who would nsdap run? Duesterberg? or Goering?
# Goering runs, essentially as a proxy for Hitler, who is now stateless.

Many are calling for us to support the incumbent Hindenburg, despite his well-known reactionary tendencies. Is he truly the best bulwark against Hitler's ascension? On the other hand, many in our party are calling for Woodsworth to run again, but he is reluctant.

[? if pcc_relation >= 50 : Another strange possibilty is an united front with the Communists, either to support Thälmann or our own candidate. ?]


- @support_hindenburg: Support Hindenburg.
- @support_woodsworth: Run Woodsworth of the CCF.
- @support_thalmann: Support Ernst Thälmann of the PCC.

